metadata.name: Kometh #1
metadata.description: Kometh is a Web3 comic publishing platform to help you publish and sell digital comics directly to your fans. 'Garden Point' is a new and exciting comic that takes readers on a journey to a dystopian future where corporations rule and magic is the key to survival. The comic is written by  Eisner Award winning comic writer Paul Jenkins, who is known for his work on popular titles such as 'The Inhumans',  'Wolverine: Origin' and 'Hellblazer.' With Jenkins' mastery of the comic medium, readers can expect a thrilling and captivating read filled with imaginative world-building and engaging characters.
